Notes:  This was sent to me on a dvd.  I can not remember who sent me the dvd, and the
        only source information given was that this was a soundboard.  The previous 
		circulating source was missing the end of Harpua and the encores.  This source 
		has the same cut in Stash, but unlike the other source, this one is cut at the 
		beginning of Hold Your Head Up, has a complete Harpua and has the encores.  I have 
		not touched the music in anyway, all I have done is change the file names to a more 
		conventional naming standard and generated checksums.
